==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Potentially
<hw>Po*ten"tial*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>With power; potently.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>In a potential manner; possibly, not
positively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The duration of human souls is only <qex>potentially</qex>
infinite.</q> <rj><qau>Bentley.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Potentiate</ent>⟦br⟧
